 spend the trust account, or issue more shares with a claim on it.=09For so=
mewhat perplexing reasons, Canna Global did a deal with a company called Li=
queous LP in which Liqueous paid roughly $1.25 million to extinguish some o=
f Canna=E2=80=99s debt, and Canna =E2=80=9Cagreed to issue 1,544,531 new sh=
ares of Class A common stock to Liqueous at a future date.=E2=80=9D=09And t=
hen, Canna Global says, Liqueous turned around, tricked its transfer agent =
