44 million more, which=C2=A0is plenty; the stock trades at like $25 per sha=
re, so that=E2=80=99s like a billion dollars of financing room.=E2=80=9D An=
d then the stock goes to $5 and it=E2=80=99s not enough.=09If it needs mone=
y, it needs money=C2=A0right now. If a bank announces =E2=80=9Cwe=E2=80=99r=
e going to raise money as soon as we get this shareholder vote,=E2=80=9D it=
 is not going to last until the shareholder vote.

