<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It might be=C2=A0<em>impossible=C2=A0</em>for =
the US Securities and Exchange Commission to write new rules for crypto? We=
 have <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35947004.223=
415/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDktMTM=
vY3J5cHRvLXdhbnRzLXNvbWUtc2VjLXJ1bGVzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA3MDMyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJn=
