itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">
The point</a> of the current Supreme Court=E2=80=99s restrictions on rulema=
king is that it wants elected lawmakers in Congress, not bureaucrats at the=
 regulatory agencies, to make the rules.=C2=A0</p>
