<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Ultimately it makes sense that, if Skydance is=
 willing to pay Redstone more for her voting control of Paramount than it w=
ill pay the nonvoting shareholders, it should also take the risk that a cou=
rt will find that unfair. To get a deal done, you have to give Redstone a s=
weetener, and you have to let her keep it.</p>
